English: Please connect to your hardware wallet
Chinese: 请连接到您的硬件钱包

English: Ledger user, connect and unlock your device
Chinese: Ledger 用户，连接并解锁你的设备

English: Trezor user, just connect your device
Chinese: Trezor用户，请先连接您的设备

English: No device found, please check the connection and try again
Chinese: 没有发现任何设备，请检查连接并重试

English: * Please unlock your device open the bitcoin wallet on the device
Chinese: *请解锁您的设备，打开设备上的比特币钱包

English: Please enter your PIN code according to the keyboard of the device
Chinese: 请根据设备上的键盘输入您的密码

English: Show the address QR Code to the camera
Chinese: 请向相机展示您的地址二维码

English: The address does not match selected coin
Chinese: 地址与选中的币种不匹配

English: Connection lost, please check your device
Chinese: 连接中断，请检查您的设备

English: Please connect your device and confirm the transaction on the device
Chinese: 请连接您的设备并在设备上确认交易

English: The signed transaction has been successfully sent, waiting for confirmations
Chinese: 签名完成的交易已成功发送，正等待确认

English: The transaction has been rejected by hardware, please try again
Chinese: 交易被硬件拒绝，请再试一次

English: Set a PIN to lock the application
Segwit address saves a certain miner fee for bitcoin transaction
Chinese: 隔离见证地址能为每一笔BTC交易节省一定矿工费

English: To turn off lock app feature, please enter your current PIN code
Chinese: 要关闭锁应用应用功能，请输入当前PIN码

English: Network error, check your network and try again
Chinese: 网络错误，请检查网络后重试

English: The wallet is full, can’t join it anymore.
Can’t add more addresses, there are already 20 unused addresses
Chinese: 无法增加更多地址，当前已有20个未使用地址

English: {{value}} is under maintenance now, please try again after the maintenance
Chinese: {{value}}正在维护中，请再维护完成后再尝试

English: Server error, please try again later
Chinese: 服务器错误，请稍后重试

English: Request too frequent, please try again later
Chinese: 请求过于频繁，请稍后再试

English: The corresponding shared wallet already exists, please import in another device
Chinese: 该私钥对应的共享钱包已存在，请换一台设备导入

English: The token contract does not allow this transaction
Chinese: 该代币合约不允许发送该交易

English: Gas Price too high, better be less than 100 gwei
Chinese: Gas Price太高，建议小于100 gwei

English: Gas Price too low, should be higher than 1 gwei
Chinese: Gas Price太低，建议大于1 gwei

English: Small dust input in the wallet, not all funds can be sent.
Chinese: 钱包中有少量Dust余额，无法发送所有资金

English: You can also use the following email address to contact us
Chinese: 您可复制下方地址，直接联系我们

English: A new address has been generated
Turn off Segwit Address in Home -> Me to use normal address
Chinese: 在首页->我的将隔离见证地址关闭，就可以使用常规地址了

English: After turned on, the default receiving address of current wallets and future wallets will be segwit address
Chinese: 开启之后，当前所有钱包以及新建钱包的默认收款地址将使用隔离见证地址
